GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
New Delhi, the 20th January, 1957.
The undersignbd is directed to inform Members of
the Council of Ministers that Shri Raj Bahadur, Minister
in the Ministry of Communications will henceforth be
designated as Minister of Communications. The Department
of Civil Aviation will, however, continue in the charge
of Shri H. V. Pataskar, Minister of Legal Affairs and
Civil Aviation.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
